<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM7.4">
<l>cantira maṇṭalampōṟ ṟāmō taraṉkaiyi</l>
<l>lantara moṉṟiṉṟi yēṟi yavaṉceviyil</l>
<l>mantiraṅ koḷvāyē pōlum valampuriyē</l>
<l>yintiraṉu muṉṉōṭu celvattuk kēlāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O right-spiralled [conch]! It seems that you settled in Dāmodara’s hand</l>
<l>without the least gap, like the orb of the moon,</l>
<l>and hold deliberations [with Him] at His ear!</l>
<l>Even Indra will not equal you in wealth!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
